<h5 id="subject_1079670">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=120911.msg1079670#msg1079670" rel="nofollow">Re: 【安科】用各种TRPG规则里的角色来当从者打一架如何？</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1079670'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1079670'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #27 于:</strong> 2020-10-15, 周四 21:52:51 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_1079670_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
